------------------------
Bottle shader and script by Lexpartizan
Licensed under MIT License
-------------------------
Scientist, guard, class-D, MTF and
Chaos insurgency models are made
by PurpleGoop and rigged by DrPri
Room textures by Foodeater / Jamie
License: CC-BY-SA 4.0
------------------------
Light Containment Zone Ambient by Jacek \"Fragik\" Rogal
License: CC-BY-SA 4.0
------------------------
SCP-173 (version 2) - Aruspice (model, textures),
Shakles (rig, animation), PixelPuffin (concept art)
License: SCP-Wiki CC-BY-SA 3.0
------------------------
SCP-650 - Shadowscale(model, textures)
License: SCP-Wiki CC-BY-SA 3.0
------------------------
SCP-914 - Apocryphos (model, texture, rig and
animations), Aruspice (new dial model and textures)
License: SCP-Wiki CC-BY-SA 3.0
------------------------
SCP-983 item - Aruspice (model, textures, rig, animation)
License: SCP-Wiki CC-BY-SA 3.0
-----------------------
SCP-939 - Apocryphos (model), Shadowscale (textures),
Shakles (rig and animation)
License: SCP-Wiki CC-BY-SA 3.0
-----------------------
PDA item - Model and textures by Shadowscale
License: SCP-Wiki CC-BY-SA 3.0
-----------------------
Agent model uses SCP: Unity guard
model with MTF animations.
SCP Security Guard -
Shadowscale (model, textures),
Shakles (rig, animation)
License: SCP-Wiki CC-BY-SA 3.0
-----------------------
Small elevator model
(used in SCP-938 containment chamber
and Gates B and C),
SCP-686 model, hanging light
and Surface Zone
are made by pop_pop_icard
License: SCP-Wiki CC-BY-SA 3.0
-----------------------
Crowbar and power generator models
used from PolyHaven.
-----------------------
SCP-347 model is made using Makehuman model.
